QUASIONEDIMENSIONAL
GAS
FLOW
WITH
APPLIED
ELECTRICAL
AND
MAGNETIC
FIELDS
IN
THE
LAST
CASE
ATTRACTIVE
POSSIBILITIES
ARE
FOUND
FOR
CONTROLLED
ACCELERATION
OR
DECELERATION
OF
GAS
AT
SUBSONIC
AND
SUPERSONIC
SPEEDS
EVEN
IN
CONSTANTAREA
CHANNELS
THE
